fr.inria.atlanmod.neoemf.data.store

Class AbstractDirectWriteStore<P extends PersistenceBackend>

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.inria.atlanmod.neoemf.data.store.AbstractPersistentStore
      • fr.inria.atlanmod.neoemf.data.store.AbstractDirectWriteStore<P>
  • Type Parameters:
    P - the type of the supported PersistenceBackend
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    DirectWriteStore, PersistentStore, InternalEObject.EStore
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DirectWriteBlueprintsStore, DirectWriteHBaseStore, DirectWriteMapDbStore

    public abstract class AbstractDirectWriteStore<P extends PersistenceBackend>
extends AbstractPersistentStore
implements DirectWriteStore
    An abstract DirectWriteStore that redirects certain methods according to the instance of the encountered EStructuralFeature. If the subclass does not re-implement the inherited methods of EMF, the call is automatically redirected to the associated method that begins with the same name.
